data.description: Classic Wolflin Beauty!! Don't miss this spacious four bedroom, four bathroom home in the heart of Wolflin, on one of the most beautiful brick-lined streets in Amarillo. This property features two large living areas, two dining areas, and two bedrooms with ensuite bathrooms as well a flex space that can be used as an office, craft room, or another bedroom. The back patio offers a relaxing oasis for mornings or evenings! Schedule your private tour of this wonderful home today!
